de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.base.impl

Class FactoryWorkspace

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.base.impl.FactoryWorkspace

  • public class FactoryWorkspace
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory workspace maps feature model formats to a feature model factory. This way it can be ensured that a specific factory is used when reading from a certain file type.
    Author:
    Sebastian Krieter
